oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Billy Block's Western Beat Songwriter Showcase (Jan. 6)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Fosson, Mark, 1950-2018; Waldman, Wendy; Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: One color window card (brown on white) announcing Billy Block's Western Beat Songwriter Showcase featuring Mark Fosson, Wendy Waldman, 5 Wheel Drive, John Stowers, Debra Davis, John Herron, Cindy Kalmenson, Michael Eisenberg, Lenny McDaniel, and Mike Brewster hosted by Edward Tree at Highland Grounds on January 6. Poster features a metal photoplate of the Western Beat logo.
